Key - [ ] brackets denote required features
      ( ) brackets denote desired features
Simulation Requirements:
[ ] GET operator
[ ] ADD operator
[ ] Instruction Fetcher (basically reads instructions in from a file)
GUI Reqirements:
[ ] Zoom functionality
[ ] Drag and drop of interfaces
[ ] Display nested component graphs
  [ ] Minimize/maximize buttons for nested graphs
[ ] Hover information
  [ ] Highlight connected inputs/outputs
( ) Step by step execution GUI
( ) Log of graph activity GUI
( ) Interface for changing component parameters via GUI
Internal Requirements:
[ ] Nested component graphs
[ ] Topological sort and execute graph
( ) Store component graph in XML
Assembler Requirements:
[ ] Define the instruction set
